`,r.jsx(n.p,{children:r.jsx(n.strong,{children:"MCP is a standard way for AI applications to connect to external tools and context."})}),`
`,r.jsx(n.p,{children:"Instead of every AI app inventing its own custom integration format, an MCP server exposes capabilities through a shared protocol. An AI client can connect to that server and discover what it provides."}),`
`,r.jsx(n.p,{children:"MCP servers commonly expose three kinds of things:"}),`
